        <section id="recommendations">
            <h2>Places I Recommend</h2>
            <div class="recommendation">
                <h3>1. Bali, Indonesia</h3>
                <p>A tropical paradise! Bali offers stunning beaches, vibrant culture, and serene landscapes. I highly recommend staying at <strong>The Ubud Village Resort</strong>, a perfect retreat for relaxation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="recommendation">
                <h3>2. Kyoto, Japan</h3>
                <p>For a deep cultural experience, Kyoto is unmatched. The temples, gardens, and traditional teahouses are magical. I had an amazing stay at <strong>Gion Hatanaka</strong>, a ryokan that gives you a true Japanese experience.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="avoid">
            <h2>Places I Wouldn't Stay Again</h2>
            <div class="avoid">
                <h3>1. Paris, France</h3>
                <p>Although Paris is beautiful, I had an underwhelming stay at <strong>Hotel XYZ</strong>. The location was far from major attractions, and the service left a lot to be desired.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="avoid">
                <h3>2. Bangkok, Thailand</h3>
                <p>The city is vibrant, but my stay at <strong>Hotel ABC</strong> was not up to standard. The room was cramped, and the staff wasn’t very helpful.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
